label: subject part concept scheme
definition: a SKOS concept scheme for ac:subjectOrientation

label: bark
definition: Plant tissue outside the vascular cambium as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0004518

label: twig
definition: Plant shoot axis developed from axillary buds as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0025073

label: stem
definition: Plant shoot axis that is the primary axis as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0009047

label: leaf
definition: Plant non-reproductive phyllome as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0025034

label: strobilis (cone)
definition: Plant reproductive system consisting of sporophylls as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0025083

label: inflorescence
definition: Plant reproductive shoot system containing flowers as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0009049

label: fruit
definition: Plant structure developing from a flower as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0009001

label: seed
definition: Plant structure containing dormant embryo as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0009010

label: male cone
definition: Plant strobilis bearing pollen as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0005031

label: female cone
definition: Plant strobilis bearing ovules as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0005032

label: flower
definition: Plant reproductive shoot system containing a carpel as defined by http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PO_0009046
